            "title": "哈塞特駁斥外界質疑 稱自己「夠強硬」能說服聯儲會官員",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"哈塞特駁斥外界質疑 稱自己「夠強硬」能說服聯儲會官員\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"640\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/A_AyRoylCwNSQUxk7E.pAQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY0MDtjZj13ZWJw/https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2026-01/c261db10-f26f-11f0-be6d-4142ee5c016b\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">哈塞特駁斥外界質疑 稱自己「夠強硬」能說服聯儲會官員</figcaption></div></figure></div>",
